Package: usdaplants
Title: USDA PLANTS Database
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Kieran", "Healy", , "kjhealy@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9114-981X"))
Description: A convenience data package providing the USDA PLANTS database
    as tibbles. Includes plant taxonomy, growth characteristics, and
    state-level distribution data for over 32,000 plant species in the
    United States.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0),
    tibble
LazyData: true
LazyDataCompression: xz
Suggests:
    dplyr,
    stringr,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://kjhealy.github.io/usdaplants/,
    https://github.com/kjhealy/usdaplants
BugReports: https://github.com/kjhealy/usdaplants/issues
